title: 'House of Cards' is back with new actors
text:
'House of Cards' is back with new actors Thursday, February 01, 2018 - 00:57 
Netflix’s hit series, “House of Cards”, has resumed production after a three-month hiatus. Now, the series is back with new characters, and without Kevin Spacey ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
